      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "cncf/artwork",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "In this repo, we have artwork in standard formats for the CNCF [projects](https://www.cncf.io/projects/) and programs. We prepare artwork in 2 formats (PNG & SVG), 3 layouts -- horizontal (also known as landscape format), stacked (which is closer to square), and icon (which does\u2026"
